Getting to know the enemy better-the global burden of chronic kidney disease.

Jha V(1), Modi GK(2).

Author information:
(1)George Institute for Global Health, New Delhi, India; George Institute for 
Global Health, University of Oxford, Oxford, UK. Electronic address: 
vjha@georgeinstitute.org.in.
